<item>
            <title>[SOLR-9556] Overseer can leak threads if it starts up while its parent container is shutting down</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-9556</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;See &lt;a href=&quot;https://jenkins.thetaphi.de/job/Lucene-Solr-6.x-Solaris/407/consoleFull&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://jenkins.thetaphi.de/job/Lucene-Solr-6.x-Solaris/407/consoleFull&lt;/a&gt; for an example.  OverseerAutoReplicaFailoverThread is particularly susceptible for some reason.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
